# ===========================
# Large data files — too big for plain git
#
# DO commit (small, needed on HF Spaces at runtime):
#   back-end/data/multinodeenergy_backend/   APEC CSV + fuel mapping
#   back-end/data/road_model/*.csv           small parameter CSVs
#
# Do NOT commit (large, regenerate locally):
#   back-end/data/road_model/*.xlsx          seed workbooks (~10 MB each)
#   back-end/data/road_model/leap_import_workbooks/  transport LEAP exports (~130 MB total)
# ===========================
back-end/data/road_model/*.xlsx
back-end/data/road_model/leap_import_workbooks/

# ===========================
# Static bundle IS committed — it is the deployed frontend artifact
# ===========================
